subject: Dear Sir/ma,
body:
Dear Sir/ma,
This is to inform you that you have been selected to receive a compensation $2.5MUSD from the United Nation compensation commission.
Kindly respond swiftly for details about the grant.
Regards,
Barr. Anthony Becker.

subject: Re: Dear Sir/ma,
body:
Dear Barr. Anthony Becker,

Thank you for your message. I am interested in learning more about this grant from the United Nations. Could you please provide me with more details?

Best wishes,
Stephen
